The following issue went on sale today:  Issuer:       ArcelorMittal (MT) 
Manager(s):  Commerzbank  Credit Agricole  HSBC Holdings  Societe General
Amount:      500 million euros
Coupon:      4.5 percent
Maturity:    March 29, 2018
Settlement:  March 29, 2012
 